Privacy Policy

matsumi studio (hereinafter referred to as “we”) establishes the following Privacy Policy regarding the handling of user information in the application “Tsubuyaki Diary” (hereinafter referred to as “the App”) provided by us.

1. About the App

The App is a diary application that allows users to freely record their daily events and feelings.
The App is provided for users in Japan and is operated in compliance with Japanese laws and regulations.

App Name: Tsubuyaki Diary

Type: Diary Application

Developer: matsumi studio

2. Information Collected

The App does not collect any personal information or information that can identify users.

Specifically, the App does not collect names, email addresses, location information, device information, usage history, or any other personal data.

In addition, the content of diaries entered by users is not accessed, viewed, collected, or transmitted by us in any way.

3. Data Storage

All data entered into the App is stored only in a local database on the user’s device.
No data is transmitted to or stored on external servers or cloud services.

4. Purpose of Use of Information

Since the App does not collect any user information, there is no purpose for using such information.
All entered data is used solely by the user for viewing and editing their diary entries.

5. Provision to Third Parties

We do not provide, share, or sell any user-related information to third parties.

6. Advertising and Analytics Tools

The App does not display advertisements.
The App does not use any external analytics tools or SDKs for access analysis or usage tracking.

7. Internet Communication

The App does not perform any internet communication.
Therefore, there is no risk of data leakage through external data transmission.

8. Security

The App is designed not to collect or retain user information.
Device management, such as screen locks and backups, is the responsibility of the user.

9. Compliance with Laws

We comply with the Act on the Protection of Personal Information and all related laws and guidelines.

10. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated as necessary.
Any changes will be promptly published on this page.

11. Contact

For inquiries regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us via the contact information listed on our GitHub Pages or on the app distribution page.

Established on: December 30, 2025
matsumi studio
